ce="preserve">Group C of the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup matches place from 9 to 18 June 2019. The group consisted of Australia, Brazil, Italy and Jamaica. The top two teams, Italy and Australia, along with the third-placed team, Brazil (as one of the four best third-placed teams), advanced to the round of 16.
Matches.
All times listed are local, CEST (UTC+2).
